<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA74">
<l>ōta neṭuṅkaṭalka ḷettaṉaiyu muyttaṭṭa</l>
<l>vētu niṟaintillai yeṉparāl - pētaiyarka</l>
<l>ḷeṇṇā tiṭumpaliyā leṉṉō niṟaintavā</l>
<l>kaṇṇār kapālak kamalam</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is without becoming full at all when however many flooding</l>
<l>long oceans are directed [and] poured into it, so they say – the skull lotus</l>
<l>of him with eyes that became full. What about the offerings</l>
<l>placed [there] without counting by naive women?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
